	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Dis, <tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" />, c'est quoi ton dessert préféré?<pageBreak /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="50" b="3" /><tag a="50" b="1" /><tag a="135" b="7" arg="0xcd00" /> ou bien<tag a="110" b="0" /> euh<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" /> <tag a="50" b="1" /><tag a="135" b="7" arg="0xcd01" />, <tag a="110" b="6" />?</message>
